    <div>
        <h3 class="section-heading">Our Mission</h3>
        <p>At KhumaloCraft, our mission is to connect people with nature by providing beautiful, handcrafted floral arrangements for every occasion. We strive to offer a wide range of flowers and plants that celebrate the beauty of nature, foster creativity, and promote sustainable practices.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h3 class="section-heading">Our Story</h3>
        <p>KhumaloCraft began with a simple idea: to create a local florist dedicated to showcasing the beauty and artistry of flowers. What started as a passion project quickly evolved into a thriving business, driven by our commitment to quality, innovation, and customer satisfaction. Over the years, we've grown and adapted to meet the changing needs of our customers. We've embraced new floral design techniques, expanded our product offerings, and forged meaningful partnerships with local growers and artisans.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h3 class="section-heading">Our Customers</h3>
        <p>At KhumaloCraft, we serve individuals and businesses who appreciate the value of beautifully arranged flowers. Whether you're looking to brighten your home, celebrate a special occasion, or enhance your office space, we offer a curated selection of floral arrangements to elevate your environment.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h3 class="section-heading">Our Values</h3>
        <p>Integrity, authenticity, and sustainability are at the core of everything we do. We believe in fostering a community that values the beauty of nature, supports local growers, and respects the environment. Our commitment to quality floral arrangements, ethical sourcing, and customer satisfaction guides every decision we make.</p>
